      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, cook the pasta in a pot of salted boiling water for 8-10 min or until the pasta is cooked to your taste, stirring occasionally</p>\r\n<p><strong>Drain</strong> and retain a cup of pasta water for step 7</p>",
